title: How to Travel The World & Make $$$
itunes:title: How to Travel The World & Make $$$
description:
Episode 574 - Do you want to learn how to travel the world and still make money? I usually travel around 50-60% of the year, and I have created a job to allow me to make really good money while I travel. I don't say that to brag, I say that because I am a normal guy who figured out what he wanted and did it. If I did it, you can too! In this episode, I will teach you how I did it and how to visualize and create the life that YOU want! I am in Italy right now and if you want to follow along on my travels, follow me on Instagram @RobDialJr
